      "# Sparse Attention Study",
      "",
      "Sparse attention reduces long-context compute by limiting token connections; 中文称稀疏注意力。",
      "",
      "## Mechanism",
      "",
      "线性复杂度证明给出窗口大小固定时的计算上界。",
      "",
      "## Aliases",
      "",
      "Selective attention and sparse connectivity describe related formulations. 选择性注意力是常见译法。",
      "",
      "## Limits",
      "",
      "Global tokens remain necessary when evidence is distributed across distant sections."
